product_name: Seattle Sports Dry Doc Digi 1 Case
long_description: With heavy-duty, splashproof construction, the Seattle Sports Dry Doc Digi 1 Case helps protect most iPhones and HTC models with a slim case or no case from water, sand and dust. Case features a SureGrip(TM) strap.
short_description: With heavy-duty, splashproof construction, the Seattle Sports Dry Doc Digi 1 Case helps protect most iPhones and HTC models with a slim case or no case from water, sand and dust.
